cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "memexa · 镜我: a self-hosted Chinese personal memory graph"
abstract: >-
  memexa ingests six categories of personal Chinese-language data
  (WeChat, QQ, email, browser history, AI conversations, voice memos),
  extracts entities and temporal evidence with a two-LLM gate-extract
  pipeline (gatekeeper + extractor), and exposes a query CLI plus a
  five-phase semantic-state inference workflow over a PostgreSQL +
  pgvector backed memory graph.
authors:
